nodes.name: Площадь
nodes.function: FOR(x=2030, x <= 2054, x=x + 1, AREA[x] = REVENUE[x] - OPEX_TOTAL[x] - TAX_NDPI_OIL_RATE[x])

nodes.name: Коэффициент продуктивности
nodes.function: KBMu=KH / (B_OIL * MU_OIL * (1 - WCT) + MU_WAT * WCT * 1); ЕСЛИ(L_WELL == 0, PI_WELL=HEFF * KBMu * 0.054286721 / (ln(RK / RW) + SKIN), ЕСЛИ(AN == 0, PI_WELL=HEFF * KBMu * 0.054286721 / (ln(RW * ((HEFF * HEFF + L_WELL * L_WELL) ^ 0.5 / HEFF + 1) * 0.5 / RW) + SKIN), a=L_WELL * (((RK * 2 / L_WELL) ^ 4 + 0.25) ^ 0.5 + 0.5) ^ 0.5 / 2; b=(a + (a * a - (L_WELL / 2) ^ 2) ^ 0.5) * 2 / L_WELL; PI_WELL=HEFF * KBMu * 0.054286721 / (ln(b) + SKIN + ln(HEFF * (1 / AN) ^ 0.5 / RW / ((1 / AN) ^ 0.5 + 1)) * HEFF * (1 / AN) ^ 0.5 / L_WELL)))

nodes.name: Коэффициент продуктивности
nodes.function: R=(RHO_FLUID * 10000 / pi) ^ 0.5; KBMu=KH / (B_FLUID * MU_OIL * (1 - WCT) + MU_WAT * WCT * 1); ЕСЛИ(L_WELL == 0, PI_WELL=HEFF * KBMu * 0.054286721 / (ln(R / RW) + SKIN), ЕСЛИ(AN == 0, PI_WELL=HEFF * KBMu * 0.054286721 / (ln(RW * ((HEFF * HEFF + L_WELL * L_WELL) ^ 0.5 / HEFF + 1) * 0.5 / RW) + SKIN), a=L_WELL * (((R * 2 / L_WELL) ^ 4 + 0.25) ^ 0.5 + 0.5) ^ 0.5 / 2; b=(a + (a * a - (L_WELL / 2) ^ 2) ^ 0.5) * 2 / L_WELL; PI_WELL=HEFF * KBMu * 0.054286721 / (ln(b) + SKIN + ln(HEFF * (1 / AN) ^ 0.5 / RW / ((1 / AN) ^ 0.5 + 1)) * HEFF * (1 / AN) ^ 0.5 / L_WELL)))

nodes.name: Экспортная пошлина в расчете до НМ
Дебит жидкости
nodes.function: ЕСЛИ(OPEX_FIXED > P_BUBBLE, Q_LIQ=PI_WELL * (START_PRESSURE_HORIZON - OPEX_FIXED), Q_LIQ=PI_WELL * (START_PRESSURE_HORIZON - P_BUBBLE) + PI_WELL * P_BUBBLE * (1 - OPEX_FIXED * 0.2 / P_BUBBLE - (OPEX_FIXED / P_BUBBLE) ^ 2 * 0.8) / 1.8)

nodes.name: Дебит жидкости
nodes.function: ЕСЛИ(BHP > P_BUBBLE, Q_LIQ=PI_WELL * (START_PRESSURE_HORIZON - BHP), Q_LIQ=PI_WELL * (START_PRESSURE_HORIZON - P_BUBBLE) + PI_WELL * P_BUBBLE * (1 - BHP * 0.2 / P_BUBBLE - (BHP / P_BUBBLE) ^ 2 * 0.8) / 1.8)
